  "title": "Warehouse Assistant (Forklift)",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop warehouse layout and planning.</li>\n  <li>Oversee warehouse documentation and inventory management.</li>\n  <li>Manage the Warehouse Management System (WMS).</li>\n  <li>Analyze warehouse processes, from receiving and handling to distribution and storage, to improve efficiency.</li>\n  <li>Date entry &amp; handle paperwork</li>\n  <li>Identify and report any maintenance, improvement, or repair needs to the supervisor.</li>\n  <li>Report any incidents in the warehouse to the supervisor.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to HSE and ISO standards.</li>\n  <li>Handle any additional projects or tasks as assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981| EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
